cast.overview: When the popular, restless Landon Carter is forced to participate in the school drama production, he falls in love with Jamie Sullivan, the daughter of the town's minister. Jamie has a "to-do" list for her life, as well as a very big secret she must keep from Landon.
cast.title: A Walk to Remember

cast.overview: This psychedelic tour of life after death is seen entirely from the point of view of Oscar, a young American drug dealer and addict living in Tokyo with his prostitute sister, Linda. When Oscar is killed by police during a bust gone bad, his spirit journeys from the past -- where he sees his parents before their deaths -- to the present -- where he witnesses his own autopsy -- and then to the future, where he looks out for his sister from beyond the grave.
cast.title: Enter the Void

cast.overview: Homer is an orphan who was never adopted, becoming the favorite of orphanage director Dr. Larch. Dr. Larch imparts his full medical knowledge on Homer, who becomes a skilled, albeit unlicensed, physician. But Homer yearns for a self-chosen life outside the orphanage. What will Homer learn about life and love in the cider house? What of the destiny that Dr. Larch has planned for him?
cast.title: The Cider House Rules

also_known_as: María de la Paz Elizabeth Sofía Adriana de la Huerta
details.biography: María de la Paz Elizabeth Sofía Adriana de la Huerta (September 3, 1984), better known by her professional name Paz de la Huerta, is an American actress and model. She is best known for her role of Lucy Danziger in the HBO television series Boardwalk Empire.
details.name: Paz de la Huerta
details.place_of_birth: New York City, New York, USA
